Medium des Politischen begreift. Welche spezielle Rolle kann Architektur als ein „kaltes“ Medium (Marshall McLuhan) noch spielen – neben den zahlreichen „heißen“ Medien, die dem politischen Diskurs heute Raum geben?  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aArchitecture and DesignxArchitecturexTheory. 0aArchitecture and statezAustriazVienna. 0aArchitecturezAustriazViennavSources. 4aUMBAU. 4aUM_BAU. 4aÖGFA. 7aARCHITECTURE / History / General.2bisacsh1 aAndrosch, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBalon, Andreas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCaviezel, Nott, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHeindl, Gabu, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHeinze-Greenberg, Ita, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKastner,, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKühn, Christian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNoll, Alfred J., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPrix, Wolf D., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTrapp, Harald, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aÖGFA, , eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Architecture, Design and Arts 2000 - 2014z9783110635690oZDB-23-GAA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts and Architecture 2014z9783110369595oZDB-23-DKA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG0 cprintz978303821691940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978303821551640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783038215516423Cover